data.description: Very nice partially remodeled home. Sellers have done a lot to bring this home up to date. Updated flooring and fresh paint inside and out, new fixtures, brand new dual pane windows and newer roof. Make sure to check out the oversized garage in the back yard with a new garage door. It can easily store additional vehicles. Large lot with no HOA. Close to major freeways and shopping in Desert Ridge and North Scottsdale. Your Clients will not be disappointed.
